saya berasa kesesakan dada.

1005
00:38:05,080 --> 00:38:06,040
Namun, perasaan itu hilang apabila saya mengiring.

1006
00:38:06,240 --> 00:38:07,320
Kalau begitu, tidurlah mengiring.

1007
00:38:10,480 --> 00:38:10,960
Ada lagi.

1008
00:38:11,240 --> 00:38:12,240
Saya dah tukar cermin mata baharu.

1009
00:38:12,600 --> 00:38:13,840
Sekarang saya pakai kanta sentuh.

1010
00:38:14,080 --> 00:38:15,400
Namun, jika saya tukar cermin mata baharu itu,

1011
00:38:15,680 --> 00:38:16,640
saya berasa sangat pening kepala.

1012
00:38:16,920 --> 00:38:17,800
Kalau begitu, jangan pakai.

1013
00:38:19,880 --> 00:38:20,560
Ada satu perkara lagi.

1014
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:22,560
Selepas awak hentam otak saya

1015
00:38:22,560 --> 00:38:23,480
sebelum ini,

1016
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:24,720
saya rasa otak kiri saya

1017
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:26,280
lebih bengkak daripada otak kanan.

1018
00:38:27,240 --> 00:38:28,400
Bengkak sebanyak ini.

1019
00:38:28,480 --> 00:38:29,960
Bengkak

1020
00:38:30,000 --> 00:38:30,800
sebanyak ini.

1021
00:38:30,880 --> 00:38:31,920
Mari sini, hulurkan kepala awak.

1022
00:38:32,520 --> 00:38:33,800
Saya hentam otak kanan awak juga supaya kebengkakan seimbang.

1023
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:34,320
Bolehkah?

1024
00:38:34,960 --> 00:38:35,640
Tak perlu.

1025
00:38:36,040 --> 00:38:37,080
Tak ada soalan lain lagi, betul?

1026
00:38:44,600 --> 00:38:45,040
Kak,

1027
00:38:45,400 --> 00:38:47,600
apabila saya datang untuk sapu ubat pada hari Khamis,

1028
00:38:47,960 --> 00:38:48,600
adakah awak akan berada di sini?

1029
00:38:50,040 --> 00:38:50,680
Tak tahu.

1030
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:52,960
Saya pergi dahulu.

1031
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:00,760
Teruskan lagi,

1032
00:39:01,080 --> 00:39:02,240
hanya ada beberapa ratus meter lagi.

1033
00:39:06,440 --> 00:39:07,080
Tengok!

1034
00:39:08,000 --> 00:39:08,920
Cantiknya!

1035
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:29,400
[Kenapa saya]

1036
00:39:29,680 --> 00:39:30,560
[teringin nak rasa?]

1037
00:39:38,360 --> 00:39:38,800
Tunggu sebentar!

1038
00:39:40,240 --> 00:39:40,920
Awak okey?

1039
00:39:43,400 --> 00:39:44,240
Ada darah!

1040
00:39:46,680 --> 00:39:47,280
Sekejap panas dan sekejap sejuk,

1041
00:39:47,440 --> 00:39:48,520
dawai besi pendakap mudah patah.

1042
00:39:48,920 --> 00:39:49,920
Mari, biar saya tengok.

1043
00:39:53,880 --> 00:39:54,960
Apa yang harus saya lakukan?

1044
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:01,240
Saya cuba urusnya dulu.

1045
00:40:03,480 --> 00:40:03,960
Begini,

1046
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:06,560
dawai besi tak akan cederakan mulut awak.

1047
00:40:18,320 --> 00:40:18,800
Dah okey.

1048
00:40:23,760 --> 00:40:25,400
[Kenapa tangannya panas?]

1049
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:27,440
Cikgu Ai,

1050
00:40:27,440 --> 00:40:28,080
adakah awak tahu

1051
00:40:28,080 --> 00:40:29,360
tangan awak sangat panas?

1052
00:40:31,240 --> 00:40:31,760
Jom.

1053
00:40:32,520 --> 00:40:32,920
Tunggu sekejap.

1054
00:40:34,640 --> 00:40:36,400
Cikgu Ai, awak dah demam.

1055
00:40:36,720 --> 00:40:37,920
Jadi tadi awak turun bukit

1056
00:40:38,040 --> 00:40:39,000
untuk beli ubat?

1057
00:40:40,200 --> 00:40:41,560
Namun, sekarang dah okey.

1058
00:40:41,680 --> 00:40:42,200
Jom.

1059
00:40:45,960 --> 00:40:46,520
Tunggu sebentar.

1060
00:40:47,000 --> 00:40:47,880
Saya ada satu topi lagi.

1061
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:49,000
Apa kata awak pakai juga?

1062
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:50,760
Tak mengapa, saya tak nak pakai.

1063
00:40:51,040 --> 00:40:51,520
Pakailah.

1064
00:40:59,080 --> 00:41:00,320
Letak bahagian ini ke dalam.

1065
00:41:01,000 --> 00:41:01,480
Baik.

1066
00:41:02,280 --> 00:41:03,240
Lagi baik daripada tak pakai langsung.

1067
00:41:03,600 --> 00:41:04,280
Nampak comel.

1068
00:41:09,320 --> 00:41:09,800
Jom.

1069
00:41:16,880 --> 00:41:18,080
[Selepas banyak tahun berlalu,]

1070
00:41:18,600 --> 00:41:19,520
[saya masih ingat akan]

1071
00:41:19,560 --> 00:41:20,280
[suasana ini.]

1072
00:41:22,040 --> 00:41:22,680
[Mula-mulanya,]

1073
00:41:22,680 --> 00:41:23,720
[saya ingat saya perlu]

1074
00:41:23,760 --> 00:41:25,000
[melalui malam gelap yang panjang.]

1075
00:41:25,120 --> 00:41:26,120
[Sebab kemunculannya,]

1076
00:41:26,400 --> 00:41:28,040
[angin sejuk dalam ingatan saya]

1077
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:29,160
[telah dipadamkan.]

1078
00:41:29,720 --> 00:41:30,560
[Kenangan yang tinggal ialah]

1079
00:41:30,560 --> 00:41:32,000
[cahaya bulan yang penuh di lantai]

1080
00:41:32,200 --> 00:41:33,680
[dan bayang telinga arnab yang saling bertindih]

1081
00:41:34,080 --> 00:41:35,280
[di atas permukaan salji.]

1082
00:41:41,820 --> 00:41:44,820
[Kawan tanda bintang. Padam]

1083
00:41:43,080 --> 00:41:44,000
[Berapakah ramai orang]

1084
00:41:44,240 --> 00:41:45,840
[yang tak akan berpisah dalam seumur hidup?]

1085
00:41:44,820 --> 00:41:45,740
[Padamkan kawan. Padam]

1086
00:41:47,640 --> 00:41:48,720
[Berapakah]

1087
00:41:48,920 --> 00:41:50,480
[kebarangkalian dua orang bertemu]

1088
00:41:50,680 --> 00:41:51,760
[dalam kalangan orang ramai?]

1089
00:41:54,480 --> 00:41:56,280
Hari Khamis,

1090
00:41:57,600 --> 00:41:58,600
memang saya yang bertugas.

1091
00:42:10,240 --> 00:42:11,960
[Kalau dapat tiba di destinasi akhir bersama-sama,]

1092
00:42:12,680 --> 00:42:13,960
[maka itu amat membahagiakan.]


